snippet.title: Dummy Never Fails Official Walkthrough (52 levels)
snippet.description:
This is the official walkthrough for Dummy Never Fails, a flash game developed by Tanoku.

This video shows you how to beat the 52 levels.

More on:
http://www.tanoku.com
http://www.tanoku.com/tanokublog/

To see the items locations go to:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wg5crx-vTn8

This video doesn't show you how to unlock all the dummy skins
